description: Humor on adult vs. baby doctor in pregnancy.
title: Doctor Dilemma
n_1: Mia, looking worried, visits Dr. Bean in a clinic.
c2_1: Time to see a baby doctor!
n_2: Mia looks confused, picturing a baby in a doctor's outfit.
n_3: Mia realizes the misunderstanding and chuckles.
c1_3: I'd prefer an adult doctor for me!
c2_3: Oh, right, not a literal baby doctor!
n_4: Both laugh, easing the tension in the clinic.
